sentences.sentence: E ures an up-to-date visual management of the APUs quality situation and reports results to the management.
sentences.translation: 确保生产现场的质量目视管理得到更新，并且向管理者汇报结果。

sentences.sentence: An ISS combines maintenance, logistics and access to spare equipment into a single package for both APUs and select avionics.
sentences.translation: 集成服务方案将维护，物流和备用设备使用结合到一个简单的应用支持包中，应用到辅助动力系统和选择电子设备中。

sentences.sentence: Without getting too technical, the new A-series APUs are made using a 32nm manufacturing process and each processor core on the "CPU side" of the APU has 1mb of its own Level 2 cache.
sentences.translation: 没有得到太多的技术，新的A系列的APU使用32纳米的制造工艺和每个处理器核心上的“CPU侧”的APU拥有自己的二级缓存1 MB。
